OL,7,FThe explosion prompted a huge
OL,8,Femergency service response with more
OL,9,Fthe a dozen ambulances arriving at the
OL,10,Fscene and both Cwm Taf Morgannwg and
OL,11,FSwansea Bay University Health Boards
OL,12,Fbeing placed on high alert.
OL,14,FSadly, one person died in the fire.
OL,16,FDanielle Evans, 40, was a "whirlwind
OL,17,Fof a woman who leaves a gaping hole in
OL,18,Fher family and friends' hearts".
