OL,7,FHer family described her as "an
OL,8,Fintelligent, caring and beautiful
OL,9,Fsoul".
OL,11,FThey continued: "The most important
OL,12,Fthings to her were her husband,
OL,13,Ffamily, dogs and friends."
OL,15,FIn the days following the tragedy, the
OL,16,Fcommunity raised thousands of pounds
OL,17,Fto support the businesses effected by
OL,18,Fthe fire.
