OL,4,CTreforest fire says many 'still in
OL,5,Cshock'
OL,7,FSingle mother Lucy is now focussed on
OL,8,Fthe future. Two days after the fire,
OL,9,Fshe discovered that a work space in
OL,10,Fthe upstairs of her gym on the
OL,11,Findustrial estate had become available.
OL,13,FAfter setting up her tattoo studio in
OL,14,Fthe new premises, she's now booked up
OL,15,Ffor the next two months.
OL,17,F"How does it feel to be in here and
OL,18,Fsettled again?" I asked her. "Ah so
OL,19,Fmuch better", she said. "I feel so
OL,20,Fmuch more at peace and getting back to
OL,21,Fwork is where I need to be".
